{"title":"A Folding Cargo Bike? Gocycle’s CXi & CX+ are Futuristic Foldable Cargo eBikes","link":"https://bikerumor.com/gocycle-cxi-cx-foldable-cargo-ebike/","date":1707489083000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi blue\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></p>\n<p>Coming in 2024…wait, that’s now. Well, coming <em>soon</em> in 2024, we will see <a href=\"https://gocycle.com/\">Gocycle’s</a> new <a href=\"https://gocycle.com/us/webstore/\" target=\"_blank\">foldable cargo bikes</a> with the release of the CXi and the CX+ folding cargo bikes. These new bikes are pretty futuristic looking with a host of design elements that really make them stand out from the crowd. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>They will be coming in an array of different colors, like grey, white, blue, green, orange, and yellow. Along with the colors, the models will be using a Lefty-style (righty?) front rigid fork and a one-sided rear chainstay that looks reminiscent of a BMW motorcycle’s single-sided swing arm. They will include the patented side-mounted Pitstopwheels composite wheels. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-green.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi green\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-green.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-green-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-green-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-green-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-green-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-green-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi green\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi green\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Other design highlights include no exposed cables or gears, and protective disc brake covers. Being a fully-foldable mid-tail cargo bike is unique in this space. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Gocycle’s CXi &amp; CX+ Differences</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CX-Orange.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CX+ Orange\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CX-Orange.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CX-Orange-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CX-Orange-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CX-Orange-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CX-Orange-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CX-Orange-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>(Photo/Gocycle) Gocycle CX+ Orange</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CX+ Orange\" /><figcaption>(Photo/Gocycle) Gocycle CX+ Orange</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CX+ Orange\" /><figcaption>(Photo/Gocycle) Gocycle CX+ Orange</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi blue\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-blue-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>(Photo/Gocycle) Gocycle CXi in blue</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi blue\" /><figcaption>(Photo/Gocycle) Gocycle CXi in blue</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi blue\" /><figcaption>(Photo/Gocycle) Gocycle CXi in blue</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It seems that the difference between the two models is the handlebar spec. The CXi uses Gocycle’s existing integrated Daytime Running Light (DRL) enabled handlebar. This is the same bar that can be found on their <a href=\"https://gocycle.com/us/webstore/gocycles/gocycle-g4i/\" target=\"_blank\">G4i</a> and <a href=\"https://gocycle.com/us/webstore/gocycles/gocycle-g4iplus/\" target=\"_blank\">G4i+</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-grey.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi grey\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-grey.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-grey-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-grey-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-grey-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-grey-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-grey-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>Gocycle CXi grey</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi grey\" /><figcaption>Gocycle CXi grey</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi grey\" /><figcaption>Gocycle CXi grey</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Yellow.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi Yellow\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Yellow.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Yellow-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Yellow-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Yellow-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Yellow-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Yellow-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption> CXi Yellow</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi Yellow\" /><figcaption> CXi Yellow</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi Yellow\" /><figcaption> CXi Yellow</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-white.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi white\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-white.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-white-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-white-800x450.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-white-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-white-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-white-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /><figcaption>The CXi white</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The CX+ features Gocycle’s all-new patent-pending Flofit handlebar which brings a big step in rider ergonomics and comfort. Check out this cool video of the Flofit handlebar in action <a href=\"https://youtu.be/nulGz_duRQ0?si=fFpk0dyQNUXhE2Hz\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>More About the Flofit Handelbar</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Front-motor-hub.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi Front motor hub\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Front-motor-hub.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Front-motor-hub-297x139.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Front-motor-hub-800x373.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Front-motor-hub-120x56.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-Front-motor-hub-768x358.jpeg 768w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>FloFit handlebar and side-mounted Pitstopwheels</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi Front motor hub\" /><figcaption>FloFit handlebar and side-mounted Pitstopwheels</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi Front motor hub\" /><figcaption>FloFit handlebar and side-mounted Pitstopwheels</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Gocycle’s all-new Flofit handlebar, which comes exclusively on the CX+, can put the rider in an upright riding position or a slightly more aggressive forward-centric position with the flip of a lever right at the rider’s fingertip. The bar is adjustable in reach, height, and grip angle.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The patent-pending tech is neatly packaged within the handlebar’s body. And the optional Quad Lock mounting point makes it easy to help stow the bike away. One bolt provides easy access for the brake adjustment and tuning. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5-Speed Belt Drive</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-belt-drive-.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi belt drive\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-belt-drive-.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-belt-drive--297x139.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-belt-drive--800x373.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-belt-drive--120x56.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-belt-drive--768x358.jpeg 768w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>5-speed Gates CDX Belt drive under the patented Gocycle Cleandrive</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi belt drive\" /><figcaption>5-speed Gates CDX Belt drive under the patented Gocycle Cleandrive</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi belt drive\" /><figcaption>5-speed Gates CDX Belt drive under the patented Gocycle Cleandrive</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Both the CXi &amp; CX+ are equipped with a 5-speed Shimano Nexus internal hub. The belt drive system utilizes extended gear ranges for carrying extra loads and galloping a bit on the flats. The smooth and premium Gates CDX carbon belt drive combined with Gocycle’s patented Cleandrive system adds rider protection, provides easy cleaning, and has snazzy aesthetics.  </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Gocycle’s WingPillar Frame</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-rear-cargo-area.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi rear cargo area\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-rear-cargo-area.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-rear-cargo-area-297x139.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-rear-cargo-area-800x373.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-rear-cargo-area-120x56.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-rear-cargo-area-768x358.jpeg 768w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>Boldly designed WingPillar Frame</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi rear cargo area\" /><figcaption>Boldly designed WingPillar Frame</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi rear cargo area\" /><figcaption>Boldly designed WingPillar Frame</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Using “high-tech” composite materials, the bold-looking WingPillar Frame is built on Gocyle’s core monocoque chassis DNA. It’s been tested to meet high load and safety standards (220kg/480lbs). This means that you are safe runnin’ your errands, pickin’ up your stuff, and haulin’ your kiddos around.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The rear deck is compatible with MIK child seats and accessories. You can even get the rear deck in premium cherry and teak woods. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A Folding Cargo Bike That’s Lightweight and Stowable</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1280\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-all-folded-up.jpeg\" alt=\"Gocycle CXi all folded up\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-all-folded-up.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-all-folded-up-297x139.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-all-folded-up-800x373.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-all-folded-up-120x56.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Gocycle-CXi-all-folded-up-768x358.jpeg 768w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>Gocycle’s CXi folded up for storage or transport</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi all folded up\" /><figcaption>Gocycle’s CXi folded up for storage or transport</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Gocycle CXi all folded up\" /><figcaption>Gocycle’s CXi folded up for storage or transport</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Most cargo bikes can be bulky, cumbersome to stow, and quite heavy making them difficult to maneuver in tight spaces. The CXi takes a step to remedy these issues with a folding cargo bike design. Weighing in at only 23kg (50lbs), it becomes a portable solution tailored for tight living and storage situations. To those not familiar with eCargo bikes, that may sound heavy, but many bikes in the this space <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/rad-power-radwagon-4-e-cargo-bike-tire-stop-ride-notice/\" target=\"_blank\">weigh up to 75lbs </a>or more. That fact that this is folding, <em>and</em> that light is very impressive. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>A folding bike is more easily storable and transportable. This versatility makes packing it on a train, in the trunk of your car, or in an apartment closet.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Gocycle CXi &amp; CX+ Retail Specs</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Retail:</strong> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gocycle CXi<strong>:</strong> $6,999<br />Gocycle CX+: $7,999<br /></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Motor: Gocycle proprietary G4drive front hub motor with traction control</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Motor Drive Control: Pedal Torque Sensing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Range: Up to 80km (50 miles)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Transmission: Patented Cleandrive Shimano Nexus 5-speed w Gates Belt drive</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shifting: Gocycle electronic Predictive Shifting</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Brakes: Hydraulic disk, front and rear</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Approximate Weight: 23kg (51lbs) including kickstand &amp; pedals</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Maximum Rider Weight: 220kg (480lbs), including clothing and luggage</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Child Seats &amp; Accessories: MIK HD Compatible</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The Gocycle CXi and CX+ will be produced in small quantities. Pre-orders are open now with a refundable deposit of $499. <a href=\"https://gocycle.com/gocycle-fc/\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a> to pre-order your own. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gocycle CXi and CX+ are available now in the UK, US (excluding Alaska and Hawaii), and Mainland Europe at launch. Delivery will start in September 2024. All depositors will be updated as they get closer to production and will be able to choose between home delivery and getting your bike delivered to one of their authorized Gocycle Family Cargo dealers.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://gocycle.com/\" target=\"_blank\">GoCycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/gocycle-cxi-cx-foldable-cargo-ebike/\">A Folding Cargo Bike? Gocycle’s CXi &amp; CX+ are Futuristic Foldable Cargo eBikes</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"cd2bafee8d8b05731dd55f94104ec42eff8fa82b34ef8f44db6e7f9d42d0d6b4","category":"Cycling"}